==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Retraxit
<hw>Re*trax"it</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., (he) has
withdrawn. See <er>Retract</er>.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld>
<def>The withdrawing, or open renunciation, of a suit in court by the
plaintiff, by which he forever lost his right of action.</def>
<rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

